metadata.name: HBLK
metadata.description: If you don't know LK from Oddies Club, then you don't know what true joy or beauty is. We designed this unique 1/1 just for her Birthday in 2022. Oddies Club hosted a lovely party in their Discord and it was seriously an unforgettable night. Although this is the final design, we actually sent her a total of four versions since we couldn't make up our minds. Happy Birthday LK. You truly are a very lovely hooman <3
